00:01:40,300 --> 00:01:46,200
=Blooming Days=

16
00:01:46,400 --> 00:01:48,998
=Episode 9=

17
00:01:50,238 --> 00:01:51,437
My baby is

18
00:01:52,317 --> 00:01:53,518
a child of the He family.

19
00:01:54,518 --> 00:01:55,717
The heavens will look after him.

20
00:01:56,798 --> 00:01:58,957
Even if someone wanted to hurt him,

21
00:02:00,037 --> 00:02:01,077
it wouldn't be that easy.

22
00:02:01,598 --> 00:02:02,757
Right, Qianmo?

23
00:02:04,598 --> 00:02:05,437
Of course.

24
00:02:07,357 --> 00:02:08,397
However, it seems to me

25
00:02:08,918 --> 00:02:09,997
that you're so pale.

26
00:02:10,957 --> 00:02:12,357
You seem to be weak.

27
00:02:13,077 --> 00:02:14,198
This belly keeps growing.

28
00:02:14,677 --> 00:02:16,037
Paleness is inevitable.

29
00:02:18,517 --> 00:02:19,358
In that case,

30
00:02:19,998 --> 00:02:21,317
you shouldn't stand here.

31
00:02:21,838 --> 00:02:22,797
Go in and get some rest.

32
00:02:23,957 --> 00:02:25,037
Please allow me to see you off.

33
00:02:26,078 --> 00:02:27,198
Did I say I was leaving?

34
00:02:27,838 --> 00:02:28,998
Didn't you just say

35
00:02:29,010 --> 00:02:30,438
we hadn't seen each other
in a long time?

36
00:02:30,638 --> 00:02:32,797
Why not invite me to go in

37
00:02:32,918 --> 00:02:33,838
for a cup of tea?

38
00:02:38,677 --> 00:02:39,638
You are very busy.

39
00:02:40,198 --> 00:02:42,118
Perhaps I'll invite you for tea
again on another day.

40
00:02:43,638 --> 00:02:44,478
Why

41
00:02:45,078 --> 00:02:46,198
are you concealing

42
00:02:46,397 --> 00:02:47,397
everything?

43
00:02:47,998 --> 00:02:49,838
Is there a secret
you can't share with others

44
00:02:49,838 --> 00:02:51,118
at Langyue Hall?

45
00:03:12,237 --> 00:03:13,237
Greetings, Madam Rui.

46
00:03:16,118 --> 00:03:18,237
Ms. Lian, why are you here?

47
00:03:19,157 --> 00:03:20,877
Young Master has lifted
the house arrest on me.

48
00:03:21,438 --> 00:03:22,638
I went to Mansion to see the prince.

49
00:03:23,517 --> 00:03:24,410
Just as I left the mansion,

50
00:03:24,597 --> 00:03:26,597
I saw Ruhua ask for a physician.

51
00:03:27,677 --> 00:03:30,278
Only then we found out that
Madam Yao had fallen down.

52
00:03:30,517 --> 00:03:31,918
I was worried, so I came here.

53
00:03:33,918 --> 00:03:34,670
Where is the physician?

54
00:03:35,317 --> 00:03:37,317
The physician left
after the examination.

55
00:03:38,478 --> 00:03:39,638
I helped Ruhua

56
00:03:39,638 --> 00:03:40,517
to clean up inside.

57
00:03:40,797 --> 00:03:41,957
I was about to report it to you

58
00:03:42,278 --> 00:03:43,118
and you had arrived.

59
00:03:48,797 --> 00:03:49,677
Do you mean that

60
00:03:50,597 --> 00:03:52,237
you witnessed the physician

61
00:03:52,957 --> 00:03:54,317
treating Madam Yao?

62
00:03:54,838 --> 00:03:55,317
Yes.

63
00:04:04,397 --> 00:04:05,317
So, what was the result?

64
00:04:07,757 --> 00:04:08,718
The physician said

65
00:04:11,438 --> 00:04:12,438
Madam Yao

66
00:04:17,037 --> 00:04:17,918
was not seriously injured.

67
00:04:18,478 --> 00:04:19,597
Madam Yao was pretty lucky.

68
00:04:19,757 --> 00:04:21,130
Just a minor disturbance to the pregnancy.

69
00:04:25,077 --> 00:04:25,797
How could this be?

70
00:04:26,677 --> 00:04:27,598
How could it be?

71
00:04:29,620 --> 00:04:31,070
(Qiege Hall)

72
00:04:31,077 --> 00:04:32,278
The person living here is...

73
00:04:32,797 --> 00:04:34,237
I know. It's Madam Mo.

74
00:04:35,158 --> 00:04:37,118
She nearly had a miscarriage
because of Madam Yao.

75
00:04:37,838 --> 00:04:38,558
I'm afraid

76
00:04:39,517 --> 00:04:40,477
that she will suffer daily

77
00:04:40,477 --> 00:04:41,957
before giving birth.

78
00:04:42,118 --> 00:04:43,598
Don't pity her, Ms. Lian.

79
00:04:44,077 --> 00:04:45,357
She is a snobbish and peacockish,

80
00:04:45,357 --> 00:04:46,197
and plays the bully.

81
00:04:46,637 --> 00:04:47,677
She is not a good person.

82
00:04:48,878 --> 00:04:50,397
Is she as ruthless as Madam Yao?

83
00:04:50,718 --> 00:04:51,477
Not exactly.

84
00:04:52,278 --> 00:04:53,718
Madam Mo is foolish and weak.

85
00:04:54,150 --> 00:04:55,550
She bullies the weak
and fears the strong.

86
00:04:55,637 --> 00:04:57,718
If she harbours ill intentions towards you,

87
00:04:58,038 --> 00:05:01,158
just be unyielding and she will give in.

88
00:05:02,677 --> 00:05:03,357
Madam Mo.

89
00:05:04,077 --> 00:05:06,118
Could you return my hairpin to me?

90
00:05:09,477 --> 00:05:11,677
What? What are you talking about?

91
00:05:12,158 --> 00:05:13,517
When I left in the morning,

92
00:05:13,598 --> 00:05:15,438
didn't Banqiu find my hairpin?

93
00:05:16,758 --> 00:05:17,998
When did she find a hairpin?

94
00:05:18,558 --> 00:05:19,598
Don't make any baseless claim.

95
00:05:19,878 --> 00:05:20,998
I saw it with my own eyes

96
00:05:20,998 --> 00:05:21,998
that Banqiu found my hairpin.

97
00:05:22,318 --> 00:05:23,998
Why did you lie?

98
00:05:26,558 --> 00:05:27,878
It's just a hairpin.

99
00:05:28,438 --> 00:05:29,917
Why are you panicking?

100
00:05:36,957 --> 00:05:37,637
Very well.

101
00:05:39,077 --> 00:05:39,758
Qianmo,

102
00:05:41,038 --> 00:05:41,797
very well.

103
00:05:43,677 --> 00:05:44,278
Madam Yao.

104
00:05:44,797 --> 00:05:46,118
Please don't listen to her.

105
00:05:46,397 --> 00:05:46,718
I...

106
00:05:49,158 --> 00:05:50,758
I really had no knowledge of this.

107
00:05:51,278 --> 00:05:52,038
Don't need to explain.

108
00:05:52,477 --> 00:05:54,077
I truly had no knowledge of this.

109
00:05:54,477 --> 00:05:55,077
Qianmo,

110
00:05:56,077 --> 00:05:57,397
if there's nothing major in the future,

111
00:05:57,878 --> 00:05:58,957
you should just rest well.

112
00:05:59,677 --> 00:06:00,637
Don't have to come out again.

113
00:06:01,598 --> 00:06:02,237
Understood.

114
00:06:06,558 --> 00:06:07,118
Haiyao,

115
00:06:07,797 --> 00:06:08,838
if there's no issue,

116
00:06:08,957 --> 00:06:09,957
please rest well.

117
00:06:10,758 --> 00:06:11,957
Master has few children.

118
00:06:13,197 --> 00:06:13,878
Haiyao and Qianmo,

119
00:06:14,397 --> 00:06:16,278
you must take this seriously

120
00:06:16,878 --> 00:06:17,917
and be extremely cautious.

121
00:06:17,998 --> 00:06:18,677
Rest assured.

122
00:06:19,598 --> 00:06:20,318
I will definitely not

123
00:06:20,318 --> 00:06:21,438
let anything happen

124
00:06:21,758 --> 00:06:22,758
to Young Master's child again.

125
00:06:58,838 --> 00:06:59,517
What?

126
00:06:59,517 --> 00:07:00,838
(He Lianxin's ordinary concubine, Xu Jirou)

127
00:07:00,838 --> 00:07:01,477
(He Lianxin's ordinary concubine, Xu Jirou)
She helped you?

128
00:07:02,158 --> 00:07:02,998
Not only she helped me,

129
00:07:03,957 --> 00:07:05,517
she did it in front of Madam Rui.

130
00:07:09,038 --> 00:07:10,450
I didn't expect that
in just five months,

131
00:07:11,158 --> 00:07:12,077
she would transform

132
00:07:12,077 --> 00:07:13,598
from a defenceless fledgling

133
00:07:13,917 --> 00:07:15,077
into someone so capable.

134
00:07:17,038 --> 00:07:18,397
It's truly unbelievable.

135
00:07:19,038 --> 00:07:20,477
If she pledges allegiance to us,

136
00:07:21,118 --> 00:07:22,318
won't we be more powerful?

137
00:07:22,637 --> 00:07:23,797
However, it could be a ruse.

138
00:07:25,158 --> 00:07:26,477
We can find out

139
00:07:26,797 --> 00:07:28,158
whether it is a ruse.

140
00:07:36,118 --> 00:07:36,758
What's wrong?

141
00:07:38,957 --> 00:07:40,637
Nothing, I'm just a bit dizzy.

142
00:07:42,118 --> 00:07:43,450
You hadn't been out for several months.

143
00:07:43,998 --> 00:07:45,558
Today is the first time
for morning greetings.

144
00:07:45,917 --> 00:07:47,077
Of course you're not used to it.

145
00:07:50,838 --> 00:07:53,158
Is Madam Rui well?

146
00:07:54,957 --> 00:07:56,278
How well could she be?

147
00:07:57,438 --> 00:07:58,758
Her only son is gone

148
00:07:59,438 --> 00:08:01,758
and she has to witness Madam Yao
getting pregnant.

149
00:08:02,998 --> 00:08:03,957
Madam Yao's child...

150
00:08:05,397 --> 00:08:05,838
Yes?

151
00:08:07,637 --> 00:08:08,278
It's nothing.

152
00:08:13,957 --> 00:08:15,237
Greetings, Ms. Rong and Ms. Lian.

153
00:08:16,917 --> 00:08:19,237
Is there anything wrong with Madam Yao?

154
00:08:19,838 --> 00:08:21,450
My lady is suffering from
severe abdominal pain.

155
00:08:21,580 --> 00:08:23,270
Perhaps she's experiencing
pregnancy complications.

156
00:08:23,550 --> 00:08:24,477
Pregnancy complications?

157
00:08:24,677 --> 00:08:25,118
Exactly.

158
00:08:25,838 --> 00:08:26,718
I'm in a hurry to fetch

159
00:08:26,718 --> 00:08:27,957
Physician Zhang for her.

160
00:08:28,197 --> 00:08:28,878
I'll leave first.

161
00:08:33,197 --> 00:08:34,930
Madam Yao is experiencing
pregnancy complications?

162
00:08:39,237 --> 00:08:41,758
Xu Liangchuan never spoke nor greeted us

163
00:08:41,758 --> 00:08:43,037
when he saw us.

164
00:08:43,357 --> 00:08:44,717
However, today, he's respectful.

165
00:08:47,638 --> 00:08:48,570
(He's not being respectful.)

166
00:08:49,677 --> 00:08:50,998
(He intentionally said it.)

167
00:08:52,357 --> 00:08:53,677
(Madam Yao already had a miscarriage.)

168
00:08:54,280 --> 00:08:55,890
(How could experience
pregnancy complications?)

169
00:08:57,277 --> 00:08:58,998
(Does she intend to keep pretending?)

170
00:09:04,357 --> 00:09:06,237
- Greetings, Madam Rui.
- Greetings, Madam Rui.

171
00:09:06,917 --> 00:09:07,518
You may rise.

172
00:09:07,998 --> 00:09:08,917
- Thank you, Madam Rui.
- Thank you, Madam Rui.

173
00:09:16,998 --> 00:09:17,638
Ms. Lian,

174
00:09:18,558 --> 00:09:19,438
are you feeling unwell?

175
00:09:23,438 --> 00:09:24,277
Madam Rui,

176
00:09:25,318 --> 00:09:26,970
perhaps because I hadn't been out
for a long time

177
00:09:27,237 --> 00:09:28,237
and I'm feeling a bit drowsy.

178
00:09:31,078 --> 00:09:32,277
Winter has already ended.

179
00:09:33,078 --> 00:09:34,837
When Yao's and Mo's children

180
00:09:34,837 --> 00:09:35,717
are born,

181
00:09:36,198 --> 00:09:37,518
we can celebrate.

182
00:09:38,878 --> 00:09:39,438
Just now,

183
00:09:39,878 --> 00:09:41,518
I met Xu Liangchuan outside and heard

184
00:09:42,638 --> 00:09:44,118
that Madam Yao
had pregnancy complications.

185
00:09:48,198 --> 00:09:48,998
How severe was it?

186
00:09:49,030 --> 00:09:49,917
Did she call a physician?

187
00:09:50,277 --> 00:09:51,530
Physician Zhang has already arrived,

188
00:09:52,318 --> 00:09:54,438
but I'm uncertain about the rest.

189
00:09:59,797 --> 00:10:00,638
Could it be

190
00:10:00,638 --> 00:10:01,758
due to her fall yesterday?

191
00:10:02,558 --> 00:10:02,998
Zuiliu.

192
00:10:03,477 --> 00:10:04,558
Check on Madam Yao.

193
00:10:04,917 --> 00:10:05,398
Understood.

194
00:10:10,318 --> 00:10:11,878
You can go back
if there is nothing else.

195
00:10:12,357 --> 00:10:13,318
If you have time,

196
00:10:13,477 --> 00:10:14,758
you may visit Haiyao as well.

197
00:10:15,717 --> 00:10:16,438
- Understood.
- Understood.

198
00:10:26,078 --> 00:10:27,198
Is the medicine ready?

199
00:10:28,477 --> 00:10:30,477
Is Ruhua stalling it

200
00:10:31,398 --> 00:10:33,398
because I scolded her earlier on?

201
00:10:33,998 --> 00:10:34,878
Madam, please bear with it.

202
00:10:35,118 --> 00:10:37,797
Ruhua knows that this medicine
is crucial for you and your child.

203
00:10:37,917 --> 00:10:38,878
She didn't dare to neglect.

204
00:10:42,398 --> 00:10:43,638
Greetings, Madam Yao.

205
00:10:45,597 --> 00:10:46,198
Help me up.

206
00:10:56,677 --> 00:10:57,198
Madam Yao,

207
00:10:58,318 --> 00:10:59,758
hearing that you had complications,

208
00:10:59,758 --> 00:11:00,958
Madam Rui was very worried.

209
00:11:01,797 --> 00:11:03,318
So she specially
sent me to check on you.

210
00:11:03,717 --> 00:11:04,518
No need to check on me.

211
00:11:05,638 --> 00:11:06,670
I have pregnancy complications.

212
00:11:06,797 --> 00:11:07,878
Can she give birth for me

213
00:11:07,878 --> 00:11:08,797
or endure the pain for me?

214
00:11:18,277 --> 00:11:19,758
Since you don't need any help,

215
00:11:19,958 --> 00:11:21,318
I'll make a move first.

216
00:11:29,357 --> 00:11:30,477
Why did you hit me?

217
00:11:31,597 --> 00:11:32,677
Why did you hit me?

218
00:11:33,558 --> 00:11:34,518
Why did you hit me?

219
00:11:37,037 --> 00:11:38,157
Why did you hit me?

220
00:11:39,958 --> 00:11:41,078
Why did you hit me?

221
00:11:44,958 --> 00:11:45,837
Why did you hit me?

222
00:11:49,078 --> 00:11:50,270
I've followed you for over ten years,

223
00:11:50,357 --> 00:11:51,917
but I've never been
treated as a human by you.

224
00:11:52,357 --> 00:11:53,398
Since you treasure

225
00:11:53,398 --> 00:11:54,237
this child so much,

226
00:11:54,277 --> 00:11:55,558
I will not let you give birth.

227
00:12:10,318 --> 00:12:11,878
Madam.

228
00:12:14,118 --> 00:12:14,717
What's the matter?

229
00:12:15,277 --> 00:12:16,470
Has anything happened to Madam Yao?

230
00:12:16,837 --> 00:12:17,277
Madam,

231
00:12:17,717 --> 00:12:18,958
Madam Yao have pregnancy complications

232
00:12:19,398 --> 00:12:20,677
and she's in excruciating pain in bed.

233
00:12:21,078 --> 00:12:23,198
However, I saw...

234
00:12:23,837 --> 00:12:24,438
What did you see?

235
00:12:28,170 --> 00:12:29,157
It's okay. They're one of us.

236
00:12:29,157 --> 00:12:29,638
Just speak.

237
00:12:31,078 --> 00:12:32,118
I saw it with my own eyes

238
00:12:32,638 --> 00:12:33,398
that Ruhua actually

239
00:12:33,398 --> 00:12:34,198
put abortifacient

240
00:12:34,198 --> 00:12:35,078
in Madam Yao's medicine.

241
00:12:39,638 --> 00:12:40,277
Nonsense.

242
00:12:41,198 --> 00:12:42,477
Ruhua is her servant

243
00:12:42,477 --> 00:12:43,398
from her maternal home.

244
00:12:44,198 --> 00:12:46,878
However, I think with how Madam Yao
scolds and abuses her,

245
00:12:47,398 --> 00:12:49,118
anyone would harbour resentment.

246
00:12:49,438 --> 00:12:50,677
It's natural for her to seek revenge.

247
00:12:51,318 --> 00:12:52,078
Did you stop her?

248
00:12:52,157 --> 00:12:52,638
I didn't.

249
00:12:53,797 --> 00:12:55,237
Are you insane? Why didn't you stop it?

250
00:12:55,237 --> 00:12:56,198
I didn't want to.

251
00:12:56,878 --> 00:12:57,970
She's committed many wicked deeds.

252
00:12:58,277 --> 00:12:59,398
This is just her retribution.

253
00:13:00,118 --> 00:13:00,917
Zuiliu,

254
00:13:01,797 --> 00:13:04,398
are you absolutely sure that
Ruhua did it?

255
00:13:04,917 --> 00:13:05,638
Absolutely.

256
00:13:07,998 --> 00:13:08,558
(Impossible.)

257
00:13:09,518 --> 00:13:10,357
(Ruhua knew)

258
00:13:10,357 --> 00:13:11,597
(that Mu Haiyao's child was lost.)

259
00:13:11,878 --> 00:13:13,118
(She wouldn't do this.)

260
00:13:14,277 --> 00:13:15,198
(The child was lost,)

261
00:13:15,280 --> 00:13:17,470
(but the physician still prescribed
medicine for the pregnancy.)

262
00:13:18,237 --> 00:13:19,118
(What's Madam Yao planning)

263
00:13:19,118 --> 00:13:20,150
(with such a grand spectacle?)

264
00:13:20,277 --> 00:13:21,510
(How big of a play will she put on?)

265
00:13:21,878 --> 00:13:22,438
(Madam.)

266
00:13:23,318 --> 00:13:24,277
(Why are you hesitating?)

267
00:13:24,518 --> 00:13:25,717
(You mustn't go there.)

268
00:13:31,878 --> 00:13:33,518
Anything unusual at Luo Qinglian's place?

269
00:13:34,037 --> 00:13:34,438
Nothing.

270
00:13:35,157 --> 00:13:36,198
However, Madam, don't worry.

271
00:13:36,518 --> 00:13:37,670
Madam Rou is keeping an eye on her.

272
00:13:38,277 --> 00:13:39,037
I'm just not sure

273
00:13:39,037 --> 00:13:40,438
if Madam Rui will...

274
00:13:43,878 --> 00:13:44,558
She'll come.

275
00:13:46,237 --> 00:13:47,157
She's always yearned

276
00:13:47,157 --> 00:13:48,357
to revive the Fang family.

277
00:13:49,730 --> 00:13:51,570
Only if Young Master inherits
the title of the prince

278
00:13:52,157 --> 00:13:53,237
that her wish can come true.

