00:13:54,438 --> 00:13:56,318
How can Young Master Xin

280
00:13:56,917 --> 00:13:58,438
who hardly has any heir,
inherit the title?

281
00:14:00,677 --> 00:14:02,318
So, as long as Luo Qinglian
doesn't stop her,

282
00:14:02,917 --> 00:14:03,717
she'll definitely come.

283
00:14:15,357 --> 00:14:16,037
Thank you, Madam.

284
00:14:20,277 --> 00:14:22,597
Although I really want to kill her,

285
00:14:23,758 --> 00:14:26,398
she carries the Young Master's child.

286
00:14:41,037 --> 00:14:41,878
Madam Rui, please wait!

287
00:15:05,958 --> 00:15:06,980
The weather is getting chilly.

288
00:15:07,477 --> 00:15:08,318
You should wear a cloak.

289
00:15:33,797 --> 00:15:34,357
Young Master,

290
00:15:35,677 --> 00:15:36,998
please don't blame me.

291
00:15:38,277 --> 00:15:39,677
I know you're busy with work,

292
00:15:40,597 --> 00:15:41,078
but

293
00:15:43,438 --> 00:15:44,518
if I don't keep you by my side,

294
00:15:45,438 --> 00:15:46,477
something bad

295
00:15:46,717 --> 00:15:47,878
might happen to the child.

296
00:15:48,837 --> 00:15:49,677
Haiyao.

297
00:15:50,438 --> 00:15:51,518
We're at this point in time.

298
00:15:51,518 --> 00:15:52,480
Why are you still saying that?

299
00:15:53,198 --> 00:15:54,797
I cherish this child

300
00:15:55,198 --> 00:15:56,958
and I need this child.

301
00:15:57,438 --> 00:15:58,477
As long as you need it,

302
00:16:00,597 --> 00:16:02,277
I will endure any hardship

303
00:16:03,797 --> 00:16:05,677
just to ensure
that the child is born safely.

304
00:16:19,677 --> 00:16:20,477
Wretched maid.

305
00:16:21,157 --> 00:16:22,917
Why did you brew medicine
for such a long time?

306
00:16:23,438 --> 00:16:24,638
Just wait, I'll punish you soon.

307
00:16:37,318 --> 00:16:39,518
Madam Rui is here.

308
00:16:49,398 --> 00:16:50,277
Don't drink that!

309
00:16:54,558 --> 00:16:56,277
This medicine is
a lifesaver for Madam Yao!

310
00:16:56,758 --> 00:16:57,398
Huairui,

311
00:16:58,318 --> 00:16:59,198
what are you doing?

312
00:16:59,597 --> 00:17:00,078
Huairui,

313
00:17:00,677 --> 00:17:02,917
do you want to kill
the child in my belly so badly?

314
00:17:04,597 --> 00:17:05,037
Haiyao,

315
00:17:05,677 --> 00:17:07,958
your words come with mixed feelings.

316
00:17:09,918 --> 00:17:11,278
I genuinely wish for your pregnancy

317
00:17:11,357 --> 00:17:12,357
to proceed smoothly.

318
00:17:15,518 --> 00:17:16,197
This medicine

319
00:17:16,957 --> 00:17:17,878
is an abortifacient.

320
00:17:25,518 --> 00:17:25,957
Haiyao.

321
00:17:26,197 --> 00:17:26,638
Madam.

322
00:17:27,477 --> 00:17:28,678
Physician Zhang!

323
00:17:28,678 --> 00:17:29,197
Physician!

324
00:17:29,717 --> 00:17:30,118
Madam.

325
00:17:30,118 --> 00:17:30,557
Young Master.

326
00:17:31,038 --> 00:17:33,158
I'll take another two hours
to brew medicine.

327
00:17:33,398 --> 00:17:34,678
Is there any quick-acting medicine?

328
00:17:35,717 --> 00:17:36,118
Yes.

329
00:17:38,837 --> 00:17:40,597
However, Young Master,

330
00:17:40,597 --> 00:17:42,437
this is a dire situation for Madam Yao.

331
00:17:42,837 --> 00:17:43,798
The original prescription

332
00:17:43,957 --> 00:17:44,758
was the best solution.

333
00:17:44,957 --> 00:17:46,077
It's too late to make a new one.

334
00:17:46,717 --> 00:17:48,077
This medicine is quick-acting.

335
00:17:48,717 --> 00:17:49,237
However,

336
00:17:49,357 --> 00:17:51,798
I'm concerned that
Madam Yao's body may not withstand it.

337
00:17:52,317 --> 00:17:54,957
Physician Zhang, bring it here.

338
00:17:59,130 --> 00:18:00,270
As long as it's good for the child,

339
00:18:01,317 --> 00:18:02,518
I can tolerate it.

340
00:18:13,957 --> 00:18:14,398
Madam.

341
00:18:16,278 --> 00:18:16,998
Madam.

342
00:18:18,998 --> 00:18:19,597
Ruhua.

343
00:18:21,638 --> 00:18:22,158
Madam.

344
00:18:35,798 --> 00:18:36,670
Physician, check her pulse.

345
00:18:37,518 --> 00:18:38,118
All right.

346
00:18:52,237 --> 00:18:52,798
Young Master,

347
00:18:52,798 --> 00:18:54,798
it's fortunate that she didn't miscarry.

348
00:18:54,918 --> 00:18:55,878
Madam Yao's condition

349
00:18:56,197 --> 00:18:57,398
seems to be relatively stable.

350
00:18:59,758 --> 00:19:00,270
You may leave.

351
00:19:10,597 --> 00:19:12,717
Huairui, how would you explain?

352
00:19:13,077 --> 00:19:13,557
Young Master.

353
00:19:14,437 --> 00:19:16,197
Even if I were to
behave rudely in public,

354
00:19:17,158 --> 00:19:18,317
I would never allow Haiyao

355
00:19:18,518 --> 00:19:19,317
to drink this medicine,

356
00:19:19,918 --> 00:19:21,317
because Zuiliu saw with her own eyes

357
00:19:21,380 --> 00:19:23,660
that Ruhua, holding a grudge
against Haiyao for the harsh treatment,

358
00:19:23,678 --> 00:19:25,317
slipped in an abortifacient.

359
00:19:25,317 --> 00:19:26,038
I didn't.

360
00:19:26,638 --> 00:19:27,158
Young Master,

361
00:19:27,410 --> 00:19:28,918
I've been with Madam Yao
since I was a child.

362
00:19:28,918 --> 00:19:29,957
How could I commit

363
00:19:29,957 --> 00:19:31,118
such an outrageous act?

364
00:19:32,038 --> 00:19:32,477
Madam Rui,

365
00:19:32,957 --> 00:19:34,557
I haven't offended you in any way.

366
00:19:34,678 --> 00:19:36,518
Why are you framing me like this?

367
00:19:38,437 --> 00:19:39,437
Whether it is a framing,

368
00:19:39,678 --> 00:19:40,870
it's not something
we can determine.

369
00:19:44,437 --> 00:19:44,878
All right.

370
00:20:03,237 --> 00:20:03,878
Young Master.

371
00:20:05,077 --> 00:20:06,197
There is nothing in this potion

372
00:20:10,437 --> 00:20:11,557
that could cause a miscarriage.

373
00:20:19,158 --> 00:20:19,878
How could it be?

374
00:20:39,196 --> 00:20:40,436
Young Master,

375
00:20:40,475 --> 00:20:41,276
please believe me.

376
00:20:41,940 --> 00:20:43,420
I would never falsely accuse a servant.

377
00:20:43,436 --> 00:20:45,340
Of course you wouldn't try to frame me.

378
00:20:46,310 --> 00:20:49,796
Madam Rui, everyone feels sorry
that you have lost your child,

379
00:20:49,796 --> 00:20:53,276
but you shouldn't have tried
to harm Madam Yao

380
00:20:53,276 --> 00:20:54,196
because of her pregnancy.

381
00:20:54,400 --> 00:20:56,916
If it wasn't for the good fortune
of Madam Yao,

382
00:20:57,400 --> 00:20:59,885
you would've lost another child

383
00:21:00,006 --> 00:21:01,220
of your own, Young Master.

384
00:21:07,280 --> 00:21:08,172
Young Master.

385
00:21:08,656 --> 00:21:09,633
Please believe me.

386
00:21:10,834 --> 00:21:12,422
Haiyao is carrying your child.

387
00:21:12,853 --> 00:21:14,938
I hold no grudge against her.

388
00:21:14,950 --> 00:21:16,270
Nor do I have ill intention to harm her.

389
00:21:16,520 --> 00:21:17,000
Young Master,

390
00:21:17,320 --> 00:21:19,915
I swear I saw with my own eyes that
Ruhua put poison in the medicine.

391
00:21:20,378 --> 00:21:22,023
If I'm lying, may lightning strike me.

392
00:21:22,560 --> 00:21:23,400
Young Master,

393
00:21:23,640 --> 00:21:25,180
I was present at
Jingqiu Pavilion at the time

394
00:21:25,378 --> 00:21:26,729
and I heard Zuiliu's report.

395
00:21:27,029 --> 00:21:28,315
She's not lying.

396
00:21:28,680 --> 00:21:29,479
Who doesn't know

397
00:21:29,600 --> 00:21:30,560
that you all serve Madam Rui?

398
00:21:31,003 --> 00:21:32,279
The physician has examined the medicine

399
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:33,470
and that's a concrete evidence.

400
00:21:33,978 --> 00:21:36,777
Madam Yao is pregnant

401
00:21:36,898 --> 00:21:38,298
but she is being treated like this.

402
00:21:39,756 --> 00:21:40,675
Young Master,

403
00:21:40,915 --> 00:21:42,804
we implore you to stand up for Madam Yao.

404
00:21:43,123 --> 00:21:43,763
That's enough.

405
00:21:57,811 --> 00:21:58,531
Huairui, rise.

406
00:21:58,965 --> 00:21:59,539
All of you, rise.

407
00:22:04,292 --> 00:22:06,333
Hui'er's matter has hurt you deeply.

408
00:22:06,573 --> 00:22:08,532
You should rest more for now.

409
00:22:09,652 --> 00:22:12,252
Let Haiyao take care
of the matters in the mansion.

410
00:22:16,412 --> 00:22:17,252
Understand.

411
00:22:38,220 --> 00:22:40,140
(Langyue Hall)

412
00:22:46,492 --> 00:22:47,453
You don't need to watch her.

413
00:22:48,372 --> 00:22:49,532
If she wanted to expose it,

414
00:22:50,213 --> 00:22:51,372
she would have said so.

415
00:23:00,853 --> 00:23:01,213
Madam.

416
00:23:01,652 --> 00:23:03,213
You really frightened me just now.

417
00:23:03,453 --> 00:23:04,853
You tested Luo Qinglian like that

418
00:23:04,853 --> 00:23:06,270
to see if she's pledging
allegiance to you.

419
00:23:06,453 --> 00:23:08,132
In case the miscarriage was exposed

420
00:23:08,252 --> 00:23:10,573
and it ruined your plan with Madam Rou,

421
00:23:10,733 --> 00:23:12,252
wouldn't it have been bad?

422
00:23:12,933 --> 00:23:13,613
Are you sure?

423
00:23:14,333 --> 00:23:15,933
If Luo Qinglian pretended
to be loyal to me,

424
00:23:16,333 --> 00:23:17,292
yet pretended to help me

425
00:23:17,292 --> 00:23:18,573
to conceal the miscarriage,

426
00:23:18,772 --> 00:23:20,532
it'd mean she had a long-term plan.

427
00:23:20,772 --> 00:23:22,292
One day, she'd be caught red-handed.

428
00:23:22,573 --> 00:23:23,853
Even if she wanted to play a long game,

429
00:23:23,853 --> 00:23:25,372
I wouldn't want to be her prey.

430
00:23:25,813 --> 00:23:26,933
In that case,

431
00:23:27,614 --> 00:23:29,254
Luo Qinglian pledged
her allegiance, didn't she?

432
00:23:31,134 --> 00:23:32,494
She is undoubtedly sincere.

433
00:23:32,933 --> 00:23:34,813
My original plan was to
kill two birds with one stone

434
00:23:35,374 --> 00:23:37,254
and at least ground Madam Rui.

435
00:23:37,774 --> 00:23:40,173
I didn't expect
that I only managed to take back

436
00:23:40,173 --> 00:23:41,413
her authority over household affairs.

437
00:23:41,734 --> 00:23:43,293
For what we need to do,

438
00:23:43,774 --> 00:23:44,693
that is already enough.

439
00:23:58,734 --> 00:24:01,094
Madam Yao, Madam Rou, greetings.

440
00:24:03,453 --> 00:24:04,293
Has everyone left?

441
00:24:06,254 --> 00:24:06,813
Have a seat then.

442
00:24:13,293 --> 00:24:13,813
Have some tea.

443
00:24:30,653 --> 00:24:32,134
I remember when we first met,

444
00:24:32,494 --> 00:24:34,614
you were just a reckless young girl
who knew nothing.

445
00:24:35,533 --> 00:24:37,854
You dared to elope and
defy the order of marriage.

446
00:24:38,453 --> 00:24:40,734
You always spoke your mind openly.

447
00:24:41,053 --> 00:24:42,293
In less than half a year,

448
00:24:42,614 --> 00:24:43,933
you've become so composed

449
00:24:44,293 --> 00:24:46,413
that you could even hide
Young Master and Madam Rui.

450
00:24:47,413 --> 00:24:48,894
People have to grow after all.

451
00:24:50,053 --> 00:24:52,218
It's just that I'm a bit smarter
than others.

452
00:24:53,772 --> 00:24:54,613
How clever are you?

453
00:24:56,532 --> 00:24:57,733
What do you think about this matter?

454
00:24:58,892 --> 00:25:00,453
My opinion doesn't matter.

455
00:25:01,093 --> 00:25:01,933
The important thing is

456
00:25:02,492 --> 00:25:03,132
I

457
00:25:04,492 --> 00:25:05,750
shouldn't be thinking about anything.

458
00:25:08,412 --> 00:25:11,053
There aren't many smart
people like you nowadays.

459
00:25:12,153 --> 00:25:13,553
Am I right, Rou?

460
00:25:18,053 --> 00:25:20,813
Yes, such people are rare.

461
00:25:22,892 --> 00:25:24,973
All right, it's getting late.

462
00:25:25,333 --> 00:25:26,172
You should also go back.

463
00:25:27,172 --> 00:25:28,772
Come by when you have time.

464
00:25:30,372 --> 00:25:30,933
By the way,

465
00:25:31,372 --> 00:25:34,292
regarding the matter of having
my elder brother take charge of the treasury,

466
00:25:34,652 --> 00:25:35,892
I can barely agree.

467
00:25:36,333 --> 00:25:38,613
However, I heard
that there seem to be many people

468
00:25:39,012 --> 00:25:40,213
who are unwilling to repay the debts.

469
00:25:41,053 --> 00:25:42,412
Even Young Master is at a loss.

470
00:25:44,093 --> 00:25:45,532
I do have a solution for this.

471
00:25:49,093 --> 00:25:50,372
You've been here for a while.

472
00:25:51,093 --> 00:25:52,532
I wonder what you've learnt.

473
00:25:54,459 --> 00:25:55,299
Which one are you best at?

474
00:25:56,659 --> 00:25:57,738
Of course it's

475
00:25:58,933 --> 00:26:00,012
knowing when to give up.

476
00:26:02,492 --> 00:26:03,892
Is it knowing when to give up

477
00:26:04,280 --> 00:26:05,892
or are you using retreat
as a means to advance?

478
00:26:09,892 --> 00:26:11,132
I believe you're tired.

479
00:26:11,412 --> 00:26:14,252
On another day,
come to Xiyan Tower for a chat.

480
00:26:15,693 --> 00:26:16,492
Take care.

481
00:26:28,853 --> 00:26:29,613
A spider?

482
00:26:30,573 --> 00:26:31,772
What does this mean?

483
00:26:36,573 --> 00:26:38,093
A spider weaves its web on the eaves,

484
00:26:38,530 --> 00:26:40,270
so that it can disguise
itself as a mountain insect.

485
00:26:41,292 --> 00:26:43,012
What the spider excels at the most

486
00:26:43,012 --> 00:26:44,333
is patience and biding its time.

487
00:26:47,492 --> 00:26:49,172
Could she have known that you...

488
00:26:52,093 --> 00:26:54,733
Could Mu Haiyao have risen to power

489
00:26:55,652 --> 00:26:58,093
by not solely relying on the Mu family?

490
00:27:02,772 --> 00:27:03,252
Ms. Lian.

491
00:27:05,292 --> 00:27:06,733
Ms. Lian, I was looking for you.

492
00:27:07,093 --> 00:27:07,813
What's the matter?

493
00:27:13,944 --> 00:27:15,105
Ms. Lian.

494
00:27:26,218 --> 00:27:27,699
If I remember correctly,

495
00:27:28,653 --> 00:27:30,134
you just mentioned your busy schedule.

496
00:27:30,653 --> 00:27:31,293
Well,

497
00:27:31,974 --> 00:27:33,774
did I owe the treasury money?

498
00:27:34,734 --> 00:27:35,693
I did say that,

499
00:27:36,573 --> 00:27:37,374
but I also said

500
00:27:37,933 --> 00:27:38,573
that you

501
00:27:40,614 --> 00:27:42,333
should obediently wait for
me at Lianwei Residence.

502
00:27:44,453 --> 00:27:46,134
What do you want to
do in bright daylight?

503
00:27:48,533 --> 00:27:49,134
Who says that

504
00:27:49,974 --> 00:27:52,573
conversations can only happen at night?

505
00:27:55,894 --> 00:27:57,453
Girl, are you thinking...

506
00:27:59,933 --> 00:28:01,293
I don't have anything

507
00:28:01,293 --> 00:28:02,293
to talk to you about.

508
00:28:02,653 --> 00:28:04,254
You don't, but I do.

509
00:28:05,453 --> 00:28:06,653
First, we should talk about

510
00:28:06,974 --> 00:28:08,173
the matter from earlier on.

511
00:28:08,453 --> 00:28:09,573
The matter from earlier on?

512
00:28:09,933 --> 00:28:11,132
You already knew?

513
00:28:11,532 --> 00:28:12,053
Girl,

514
00:28:14,412 --> 00:28:16,853
you aren't hiding anything from me,
are you?

515
00:28:18,333 --> 00:28:19,292
Young Master, please behave.

516
00:28:19,973 --> 00:28:20,652
Behave?

517
00:28:20,892 --> 00:28:21,933
Ask around.

518
00:28:21,933 --> 00:28:22,733
If I ever behaved,

519
00:28:22,733 --> 00:28:23,933
I wouldn't have been He Lianxin.

520
00:28:24,412 --> 00:28:25,892
You're now my servant-concubine.

521
00:28:26,573 --> 00:28:28,613
Do you really think
being a servant-concubine is so easy?

522
00:28:32,280 --> 00:28:34,000
We had a gentlemen's agreement.
You can't touch me.

523
00:28:34,012 --> 00:28:34,853
An agreement?

524
00:28:35,093 --> 00:28:35,973
What have you done for me?

525
00:28:36,492 --> 00:28:37,573
Guessing my father's intentions

526
00:28:37,573 --> 00:28:38,693
or helping me to recover the debt?

527
00:28:40,652 --> 00:28:41,172
I...

528
00:28:45,573 --> 00:28:46,733
I, He Lianxin,

529
00:28:47,492 --> 00:28:49,292
never engage in unprofitable deals.

530
00:28:50,772 --> 00:28:52,132
Even if I miscalculated this time

531
00:28:52,412 --> 00:28:53,372
and placed the wrong bet,

532
00:28:56,213 --> 00:28:57,573
I can't let myself

533
00:28:58,172 --> 00:29:00,132
